{"title":"Intoxicacion Cocaina ACV iPad","guid":"","filepath":"/Users/criaah/Vault/📚 Resources/Mapas-Mentales/Entidades clínicas/Cardiología/Intoxicacion Cocaina ACV iPad.smmx","root":{"id":"0","parent":"-1","text":"Intoxicación por Cocaína\\N— Manejo y ACV","guid":"-N7i6JsOosgqjnqZQynVcQ","children":[{"id":"1","parent":"0","text":"Farmacología","guid":"","children":[{"id":"2","parent":"1","text":"Mecanismo\\Nde acción","guid":"z_UHxmuzrAtOAXR3AJNUCQ","children":[{"id":"3","parent":"2","text":"Bloqueo recaptación dopamina, noradrenalina, serotonina","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"4","parent":"2","text":"Bloqueo canales Na+ → efecto anestésico local","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"5","parent":"2","text":"Estimulación simpática MASIVA → catecolaminas ↑","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"6","parent":"1","text":"Farmacocinética","guid":"","children":[{"id":"7","parent":"6","text":"Vía inhalada → pico 1-5 min, duración 15-30 min","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"8","parent":"6","text":"Vía intranasal → pico 15-30 min, duración 60-90 min","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"9","parent":"6","text":"Vía oral → pico 60-90 min, duración variable","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"10","parent":"6","text":"Vida media plasmática → 0.5-1.5 horas","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"11","parent":"6","text":"Metabolismo hepático → benzoilecgonina (metabolito principal)","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"12","parent":"1","text":"Cocaetileno","guid":"","children":[{"id":"13","parent":"12","text":"Metabolito activo → cocaína + alcohol","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"14","parent":"12","text":"Vida media MÁS LARGA (3-5x) → mayor cardiotoxicidad","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"15","parent":"12","text":"Potencia letalidad del consumo concomitante","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"16","parent":"0","text":"Presentación\\NClínica Aguda","guid":"JQIqJPgRfibhGH1_dTyqpA","children":[{"id":"17","parent":"16","text":"Manifestaciones\\Nsimpáticas","guid":"GdVrmkNTQQZ28JJ97cYd1g","children":[{"id":"18","parent":"17","text":"Taquicardia, hipertensión arterial","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"19","parent":"17","text":"Midriasis bilateral","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"20","parent":"17","text":"Diaforesis, temblor","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"21","parent":"17","text":"HIPERTERMIA → factor pronóstico CLAVE","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"22","parent":"16","text":"Manifestaciones\\Nneurológicas","guid":"nXTf3_aGWPumSrUWX3qvyw","children":[{"id":"23","parent":"22","text":"Agitación psicomotora severa","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"24","parent":"22","text":"Paranoia, alucinaciones (auditivas frecuentes)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"25","parent":"22","text":"Convulsiones → generalizadas, primeras 2 horas","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"26","parent":"22","text":"Formicación (sensación de insectos en piel)","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"27","parent":"16","text":"Manifestaciones\\Ncardiovasculares","guid":"cKDYEo5TWBOog5yAaPrOsQ","children":[{"id":"28","parent":"27","text":"SCA → vasoespasmo coronario + trombosis","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"29","parent":"27","text":"Arritmias → taquicardia QRS ancho, FV, TV","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"30","parent":"27","text":"Disección aórtica","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"31","parent":"27","text":"Miocarditis aguda","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"32","parent":"16","text":"Manifestaciones cerebrovasculares → VER SECCIÓN ACV","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"33","parent":"16","text":"Otras\\Ncomplicaciones","guid":"ee_dhwiQziTzQTv2zUZMuw","children":[{"id":"34","parent":"33","text":"Rabdomiólisis (CPK >10.000 UI/L)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"35","parent":"33","text":"Insuficiencia renal aguda (mioglobina)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"36","parent":"33","text":"Neumotórax/neumomediastino (fumada/crack)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"37","parent":"33","text":"Isquemia mesentérica","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"38","parent":"33","text":"Perforación tabique nasal (uso crónico)","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"39","parent":"0","text":"ACV Asociado a\\NCocaína","guid":"oigXCnN43-E9I_UZyI-31Q","children":[{"id":"40","parent":"39","text":"Epidemiología","guid":"","children":[{"id":"41","parent":"40","text":"OR 2.33 (IC 95% 1.74-3.11) para ACV","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"42","parent":"40","text":"Afecta predominantemente JÓVENES (15-44 años)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"43","parent":"40","text":"Cocaína → causa frecuente de ACV en <45 años","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"44","parent":"40","text":"Puede ocurrir con PRIMERA exposición","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"45","parent":"39","text":"Fisiopatología →\\NMULTIFACTORIAL","guid":"GD_IhUgYH_meHggsG16bag","children":[{"id":"46","parent":"45","text":"Vasoespasmo cerebral","guid":"","children":[{"id":"47","parent":"46","text":"Estimulación alfa-adrenérgica directa","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"48","parent":"46","text":"Disminución producción óxido nítrico endotelial","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"49","parent":"46","text":"Hipoperfusión cortical progresiva con uso crónico","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"50","parent":"45","text":"Trombosis","guid":"","children":[{"id":"51","parent":"50","text":"Activación y agregación plaquetaria ↑","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"52","parent":"50","text":"Hipercoagulabilidad → factor von Willebrand ↑","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"53","parent":"50","text":"Endoteliopatía crónica","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"54","parent":"45","text":"Hemorragia","guid":"","children":[{"id":"55","parent":"54","text":"HTA aguda severa → ruptura vascular","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"56","parent":"54","text":"Malformaciones vasculares preexistentes desenmascaradas","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"57","parent":"54","text":"Vasculitis cerebral (uso crónico)","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"58","parent":"45","text":"Embolismo","guid":"","children":[{"id":"59","parent":"58","text":"Endocarditis en usuarios IV","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"60","parent":"58","text":"Embolismo paradójico (foramen oval)","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"61","parent":"39","text":"Tipos\\Nde ACV","guid":"o8niMgn06t9C6s9mI6HweA","children":[{"id":"62","parent":"61","text":"ACV ISQUÉMICO","guid":"","children":[{"id":"63","parent":"62","text":"Más frecuente con uso CRÓNICO","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"64","parent":"62","text":"Territorio → ACM más frecuente","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"65","parent":"62","text":"Vasoespasmo + trombosis in situ","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"66","parent":"62","text":"Considerar etiología embólica cardíaca","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"67","parent":"61","text":"ACV HEMORRÁGICO","guid":"","children":[{"id":"68","parent":"67","text":"Más frecuente con uso AGUDO","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"69","parent":"67","text":"HSA → asociada a aneurismas/MAV preexistentes","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"70","parent":"67","text":"HIC → ganglios basales, tálamo, cerebelo","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"71","parent":"67","text":"Mayor mortalidad que ACV hemorrágico no-cocaínico","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"72","parent":"39","text":"Diagnóstico","guid":"","children":[{"id":"73","parent":"72","text":"TC cerebro sin contraste → PRIMERA línea","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"74","parent":"72","text":"Angio-TC → descartar aneurisma, vasoespasmo","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"75","parent":"72","text":"RM cerebral → complementar en subagudo","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"76","parent":"72","text":"Screening toxicológico → benzoilecgonina en orina (+72h)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"77","parent":"72","text":"Ecocardiograma → descartar endocarditis, trombo, FOP","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"78","parent":"72","text":"Estudio hematológico → trombofilia si recurrente","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"79","parent":"39","text":"Manejo del ACV\\Npor cocaína","guid":"0JogM9LxLpwG6RMf7SNDKQ","children":[{"id":"80","parent":"79","text":"ACV ISQUÉMICO","guid":"","children":[{"id":"81","parent":"80","text":"Trombólisis IV (alteplase)\\N→ CONTROVERSIAL","guid":"wyH-Un3eDndbATOPc3Mv9Q","children":[{"id":"82","parent":"81","text":"No contraindicación absoluta según AHA","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"83","parent":"81","text":"Riesgo teórico → HTA, coagulopatía","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"84","parent":"81","text":"Ventana 4.5h estándar → individualizar","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"85","parent":"81","text":"PRECAUCIÓN → mayor riesgo transformación hemorrágica","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"86","parent":"80","text":"Trombectomía mecánica → si oclusión gran vaso","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"87","parent":"80","text":"Control PA → objetivo <185/110 pre-trombólisis","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"88","parent":"80","text":"Antiagregación → cautela, evaluar caso a caso","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"89","parent":"79","text":"ACV\\NHEMORRÁGICO","guid":"4KmW3IJy2akk-mbdt6JDXA","children":[{"id":"90","parent":"89","text":"Control PA AGRESIVO → labetalol IV, nicardipino","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"91","parent":"89","text":"EVITAR betabloqueadores puros","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"92","parent":"89","text":"Neurocirugía → según indicación estándar","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"93","parent":"89","text":"Angiografía → si sospecha aneurisma/MAV","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"94","parent":"89","text":"Corrección coagulopatía si presente","guid":"","children":[]}]}]}]},{"id":"95","parent":"0","text":"Manejo General\\Nde la Intoxicación","guid":"nYUkCr8cXPLDfZGkxNOFJA","children":[{"id":"96","parent":"95","text":"ABCDE y\\Nestabilización","guid":"Rzn8x3BbiBHPusoITxV1Lg","children":[{"id":"97","parent":"96","text":"Vía aérea → IOT si GCS <8 o convulsiones refractarias","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"98","parent":"96","text":"Monitorización continua → ECG, oximetría, temperatura","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"99","parent":"96","text":"Accesos vasculares, análisis de laboratorio","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"100","parent":"96","text":"Screening toxicológico completo","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"101","parent":"95","text":"BENZODIAZEPINAS\\N→ PRIMERA LÍNEA","guid":"zCWyeFfVqLaoBj8l0Y6dcA","children":[{"id":"102","parent":"101","text":"Diazepam 5-10 mg IV o Midazolam 2-5 mg IV/IM","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"103","parent":"101","text":"Eficaz en 70-90% de los cuadros agitados","guid":"eWXJTYkvFqVr10o_lsDO7A","children":[]},{"id":"104","parent":"101","text":"Controlan → agitación, convulsiones, taquicardia, HTA","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"105","parent":"101","text":"Escalar dosis según respuesta","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"106","parent":"101","text":"NUNCA usar flumazenil → riesgo convulsiones","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"107","parent":"95","text":"Control\\Ncardiovascular","guid":"-RvSn8R3Qtk9OWhti7nlFA","children":[{"id":"108","parent":"107","text":"Nitroglicerina → vasoespasmo coronario, SCA","guid":"","children":[{"id":"109","parent":"108","text":"Precaución → hipotensión y taquicardia refleja","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"110","parent":"107","text":"Fentolamina → alfa-bloqueador, HTA refractaria","guid":"","children":[{"id":"111","parent":"110","text":"Poco disponible en urgencias chilenas","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"112","parent":"107","text":"Calcioantagonistas → nicardipino, verapamilo","guid":"","children":[{"id":"113","parent":"112","text":"↓ HTA y vasoespasmo, no ↓ taquicardia","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"114","parent":"107","text":"Labetalol IV → alfa/beta\\Nbloqueador combinado","guid":"sYyiSCpCQci552DvD-qFWw","children":[{"id":"115","parent":"114","text":"Controversia histórica → evidencia reciente favorable","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"116","parent":"114","text":"AHA/ACC aprueba para HTA + taquicardia en cocaína","guid":"yOyqUPlunT_agygLSNmymg","children":[]},{"id":"117","parent":"114","text":"NUNCA betabloqueadores puros → estimulación alfa sin oposición","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"118","parent":"107","text":"Dexmedetomidina\\N→ alfa-2 agonista","guid":"J8L9bVsV2XeEggau3iDzWQ","children":[{"id":"119","parent":"118","text":"Sedación sin depresión respiratoria","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"120","parent":"118","text":"Evidencia creciente en intoxicación estimulantes","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"121","parent":"95","text":"Control de\\Nhipertermia","guid":"MV5dxOSqqRMK1RALHs9kcw","children":[{"id":"122","parent":"121","text":"ENFRIAMIENTO EXTERNO → primera medida","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"123","parent":"121","text":"Nebulización con agua tibia + ventilador","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"124","parent":"121","text":"Baño de hielo si T >40°C","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"125","parent":"121","text":"Antipiréticos NO son efectivos","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"126","parent":"121","text":"Monitorizar temperatura central continuamente","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"127","parent":"95","text":"Convulsiones","guid":"","children":[{"id":"128","parent":"127","text":"BZD primera línea → diazepam, midazolam","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"129","parent":"127","text":"Si refractarias → fenobarbital, propofol","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"130","parent":"127","text":"NO fenitoína → ineficaz en convulsiones tóxicas","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"131","parent":"127","text":"Descartar ACV como causa si focales","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"132","parent":"95","text":"Arritmias","guid":"","children":[{"id":"133","parent":"132","text":"QRS ancho → Bicarbonato\\Nde sodio IV (1-2 mEq/kg)","guid":"jO7bRbsUv1cZWTIvFkvCaQ","children":[{"id":"134","parent":"133","text":"Bloqueo Na+ → efecto anestésico local de cocaína","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"135","parent":"133","text":"Recomendación fuerte ASAM/AAAP 2024","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"136","parent":"132","text":"TV/FV → lidocaína, cardioversión/desfibrilación","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"137","parent":"132","text":"NO usar procainamida → prolonga QT","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"138","parent":"132","text":"Corregir acidosis → mejora contractilidad","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"139","parent":"95","text":"Rabdomiólisis","guid":"","children":[{"id":"140","parent":"139","text":"Hidratación agresiva → SSF 200-300 mL/h","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"141","parent":"139","text":"Monitorizar CPK, función renal, electrolitos","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"142","parent":"139","text":"Objetivo → diuresis >200 mL/h","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"143","parent":"139","text":"Bicarbonato → alcalinizar orina (controversial)","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"144","parent":"95","text":"Sedación para\\Nagitación severa","guid":"3Sks3080tv9u7ecLSMG5bA","children":[{"id":"145","parent":"144","text":"BZD primera línea","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"146","parent":"144","text":"B-52 → Haloperidol 5mg + Difenhidramina 50mg + Lorazepam 2mg","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"147","parent":"144","text":"Ketamina IM → alternativa emergente","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"148","parent":"144","text":"Antipsicóticos → agitación/psicosis refractaria","guid":"","children":[{"id":"149","parent":"148","text":"Precaución → ↓ umbral convulsivo, EPS","guid":"","children":[]}]}]}]},{"id":"150","parent":"0","text":"Consideraciones\\NGeriátricas","guid":"EoWhYHK_B_lksHH0XM-3AA","children":[{"id":"151","parent":"150","text":"Mayor vulnerabilidad\\Ncardiovascular","guid":"Z-yyuLVxkC4FOGPCrJ8uTQ","children":[{"id":"152","parent":"151","text":"Rigidez arterial + HTA preexistente → mayor riesgo ACV","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"153","parent":"151","text":"Disfunción diastólica → menor tolerancia a catecolaminas","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"154","parent":"151","text":"Mayor prevalencia de enfermedad coronaria de base","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"155","parent":"150","text":"Farmacocinética\\Nalterada","guid":"tkYUBemFT_2oLLPJUmJbig","children":[{"id":"156","parent":"155","text":"↓ Metabolismo hepático → acumulación cocaína","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"157","parent":"155","text":"↓ Clearance renal → metabolitos activos prolongados","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"158","parent":"155","text":"Mayor sensibilidad a BZD → titular cuidadosamente","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"159","parent":"150","text":"Polifarmacia","guid":"","children":[{"id":"160","parent":"159","text":"Interacción con anticoagulantes, antihipertensivos","guid":"x5_FAJ0cIZ2ZQnuxxUZLVg","children":[]},{"id":"161","parent":"159","text":"Mayor riesgo de sangrado con antiagregantes","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"162","parent":"159","text":"STOPP/START → revisar al ingreso","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"163","parent":"150","text":"Fragilidad\\Ncomo predictor","guid":"nu6pku_HkzAFlpdCSnHhHw","children":[{"id":"164","parent":"163","text":"CFS ≥5 → peor pronóstico en ACV","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"165","parent":"163","text":"Mayor mortalidad intrahospitalaria","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"166","parent":"163","text":"Proporcionalidad terapéutica → evaluar caso a caso","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"167","parent":"150","text":"Screening\\Ninfradiagnosticado","guid":"RcpwkSd38ZtV2ZUM1Oebqw","children":[{"id":"168","parent":"167","text":"Consumo de cocaína en AM → SUBDETECTADO","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"169","parent":"167","text":"Mantener alta sospecha en ACV joven-viejo sin FR clásicos","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"170","parent":"167","text":"Solicitar toxicológico en orina siempre","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"171","parent":"0","text":"Perlas\\NClínicas","guid":"tT8JSz9fw1SyDzXEKUY0pw","children":[{"id":"172","parent":"171","text":"NUNCA betabloqueadores puros → estimulación alfa sin oposición → empeora HTA y vasoespasmo","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"173","parent":"171","text":"BZD son la PIEDRA ANGULAR → controlan agitación, convulsiones, HTA y taquicardia","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"174","parent":"171","text":"Cocaetileno (cocaína+OH) → vida media 3-5x mayor → cardiotoxicidad potenciada","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"175","parent":"171","text":"QRS ancho = Bicarbonato de sodio IV → efecto de bloqueo Na+ por cocaína","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"176","parent":"171","text":"Hipertermia NO responde a antipiréticos → SOLO enfriamiento externo","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"177","parent":"171","text":"ACV hemorrágico más frecuente con uso AGUDO, isquémico con uso CRÓNICO","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"178","parent":"171","text":"Trombólisis IV en ACV isquémico por cocaína → NO contraindicación absoluta (AHA)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"179","parent":"171","text":"En AM → siempre solicitar toxicológico en orina ante ACV sin FR clásicos","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"180","parent":"171","text":"Dexmedetomidina → sedación sin depresión respiratoria, ideal en AM crítico","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"181","parent":"171","text":"NUNCA flumazenil en intoxicación cocaína → riesgo de convulsiones letales","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"182","parent":"0","text":"Referencias","guid":"JG_4eX5dODIwBwMNSaq4YA","children":[{"id":"183","parent":"182","text":"1. Richards JR et al. Treatment of cocaine cardiovascular toxicity: a systematic review. Clin Toxicol (Phila). 2016;54(5):345-64. DOI: 10.3109/15563650.2016.1142090","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"184","parent":"182","text":"2. Siniscalchi A et al. Cocaine dependence and stroke: pathogenesis and management. Curr Neurovasc Res. 2015;12(2):163-72. DOI: 10.2174/1567202612666150305110144","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"185","parent":"182","text":"3. Fries A et al. The Diagnosis and Treatment of Stimulant-Related Emergencies. Dtsch Arztebl Int. 2025;122(26):715-721. DOI: 10.3238/arztebl.m2025.0158","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"186","parent":"182","text":"4. ASAM/AAAP Clinical Practice Guideline on the Management of Stimulant Use Disorder. J Addict Med. 2024;18(1S):1-56. DOI: 10.1097/ADM.0000000000001299","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"187","parent":"182","text":"5. You J et al. Cerebrovascular adaptations to cocaine-induced TIA in rodent brain. JCI Insight. 2017;2(5):e90809. DOI: 10.1172/jci.insight.90809","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"188","parent":"182","text":"6. Santurtún A et al. Cocaine in hospital admissions for circulatory diseases. Cardiovasc Toxicol. 2020;20(1):20-27. DOI: 10.1007/s12012-019-09537-6","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"189","parent":"182","text":"7. AHA 2023 Guideline for Management of Life-Threatening Cocaine Toxicity","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"190","parent":"182","text":"8. StatPearls: Cocaine Toxicity. NCBI Bookshelf. 2023","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},"node_count":190,"relations":[],"cross_references":[],"specialty":"Cardiología","folder":"Entidades clínicas/Cardiología","filename":"Intoxicacion Cocaina ACV iPad","id":"map_300","resolved_references":[],"title_raw":"Intoxicacion Cocaina ACV iPad"}